DLTB = Download tamilbeat
       ^   ^    ^    ^


Introduction:
Given an URL as a input, dltb downloads all the mp3 
files! 


USAGE:
./dltb <tamilbeat.com URL>


EXAMPLE:
./dltb http://www.tamilat.com/tamilsongs



==================================
Global setup:
 Set up git
  git config --global user.name "Sangeeth Saravanaraj"
  git config --global user.email sangeeth.saravanaraj@gmail.com
      
Next steps:
  mkdir dltb
  cd dltb
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:sangeeths/dltb.git
  git push -u origin master
      
Existing Git Repo?
  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:sangeeths/dltb.git
  git push -u origin master
      
